WEBVTT

00:08:56.042 --> 00:09:01.184
we can give the best of us
to protect our peoples,

00:09:01.208 --> 00:09:03.101
to protect our planet,

00:09:03.125 --> 00:09:06.125
to restore the ecosystem
that we are losing.

00:09:07.042 --> 00:09:08.958
I did that in another way, also.

00:09:09.750 --> 00:09:13.601
I used a tool that I really love a lot.

00:09:13.625 --> 00:09:17.809
It's called a 3D participatory mapping:

00:09:17.833 --> 00:09:23.268
participatory, because it can bring
women, men,

00:09:23.292 --> 00:09:25.476
youth, elders,

00:09:25.500 --> 00:09:28.684
all the intergenerational peoples.

00:09:28.708 --> 00:09:32.059
Then they use science-based knowledge,